      "rationale": "CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2024R1) operates under ISO 9001:2015 QMS. Full version-controlled simulation environment documented in SQA plan SQA-2025-001. Regression test suite of 847 cases executed; all pass. Change control records complete. Independent SQA audit completed 2025-03-15 with zero critical findings. Traceability from requirements to test cases documented."
