      "rationale": "All bench test conditions (flow rate, impeller speed, fluid temperature, hematocrit, anticoagulant protocol) documented to ASTM F1841 and ISO 10993-4. Calibration certificates for all measurement instruments traceable to NIST standards. Test matrix covers 5 operating points spanning full clinical range. Environmental conditions (temperature 37±0.5°C, pH 7.4±0.05) logged at 1-minute intervals throughout testing."
    },
    {
