      "rationale": "Iterative convergence verified by monitoring residuals (all < 1×10⁻⁶), force and moment monitors (< 0.01% change over final 500 iterations), and QoI monitors (NIH change < 0.001% over final 200 iterations). Round-off error estimated via double-precision arithmetic analysis; contribution < 0.01% of discretization error. Time-step independence study for transient impeller passage confirmed temporal error < 0.5% for all QoIs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
