      "rationale": "Independent peer review of all simulation setup files, boundary condition assignments, material property inputs, and post-processing scripts conducted by two senior engineers not involved in original analysis. Review checklist UE-CL-2025-001 completed with zero critical findings. Simulation inputs verified against source documents. Post-processing scripts unit-tested against analytical solutions. All reviewer comments addressed and documented in review response log."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
